    "description": {
      "content": "The 1Password Events API provides programmatic access to event data generated within a 1Password account. It enables security teams and administrators to retrieve sign-in attempts, item usage records, and audit events for monitoring, compliance, and security analysis. The API uses cursor-based pagination with POST requests to efficiently stream large volumes of event data.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: 1Password Support",
